@startuml
title Decorator Pattern (C_A ~ C_E)

skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor<<Component>>         #E1F5EE
  BackgroundColor<<ConcreteComponent>> #E6F1FB
  BackgroundColor<<Decorator>>         #FAEEDA
  BackgroundColor<<ConcreteDecorator>> #FAECE7
  BorderColor #4A4A4A
}

interface C_A <<Component>> {
    + add() : String
}

class C_B <<ConcreteComponent>> {
    + add() : String
}
note bottom of C_B : 핵심 객체 · 반환값 "C_B"

abstract class C_C <<Decorator>> {
    - c_A : C_A
    + C_C(c_A : C_A)
    + add() : String
}
note right of C_C : C_A를 **구현**하면서\n동시에 C_A를 **보유** → 위임

class C_D <<ConcreteDecorator>> {
    + add() : String
}
note bottom of C_D : super.add() + " + second element"

class C_E <<ConcreteDecorator>> {
    + add() : String
}
note bottom of C_E : super.add() + " + first element"

class Main {
    + {static} main(args : String[]) : void
}

C_A <|.. C_B
C_A <|.. C_C
C_C <|-- C_D
C_C <|-- C_E
C_C o--> C_A : wraps
Main ..> C_A : uses
@enduml